name: Cat Call Agent
description: Cat Call Agent is an AI-powered crypto companion within the Ink Ecosystem. Cat Call Agent serves as a unique bridge between the Ink ecosystem and its community. As an AI-powered agent with a feline persona, it plays a crucial role in making the ecosystem more accessible and engaging. Its primary function is monitoring and reporting on all significant developments within the Ink ecosystem. In the long term, we plan to become the leading AI companion for crypto analysis.
